9
00:01:08.047 --> 00:01:19.138
<v NARRATOR>Photo grew up in an ancient, airless world. For a billion years, her family quietly changed the entire planet's atmosphere.

10
00:01:19.138 --> 00:01:28.469
<v PHOTO>It took so long. We just kept making air, hoping one day it would be enough for everyone to breathe safely.

11
00:01:28.469 --> 00:01:36.680
